{"tid":494980,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手問題 - 成貓領養","createTime":"2017-12-10T08:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T15:54:01.000Z","uid":82375,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"967b8dc586593d1d556e2cd30f1af6a4fc41a2d7","tid":494980,"uid":82375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"男朋友同我都好仲意貓 想有能力既時候領養隻主子<br />\n今年置業 所有野settle 好咗 於是就plan下領養一隻主人 <br />\n後來見到有領養post出 於是聯絡個貓義工 家訪咩都做齊晒架喇 <br />\n聽個貓義工講 同胎8隻貓 佢係最尾一隻俾人領養 本身佢驚青 又細膽喇 不過領養時都預咗要花好長時間去先可以令佢放下&ldquo;介&rdquo;心 <br />\n琴日接到番屋企 困佢入籠擺係書房 等佢有d安全感 後尾見佢ok少少抱佢出黎坐訓下貓窩 點知無耐唔為意就捐落梳化底 原來係驚到要地方捐 又唔飲水唔食野 <br />\n本身見佢放鬆d會好d. 原來係搵地方收埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點算好 請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原諒我1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c12ca8b8366f8f066468da2374295a86109f6d1","tid":494980,"uid":1408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"一日半日冇野嫁喎<br />\n佢有冇去廁所飲水？"},{"pid":"903c9cae2da2dac0c51f7ca90b8165de2066295b","tid":494980,"uid":14706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:51:17.000Z","msg":"個個接返黎都係咁 比一星期佢習慣 有正常食野飲水就得"},{"pid":"d5d7cd0abcf3678978f8a22185ec4730166a6513","tid":494980,"uid":14706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"Btw唔建議困籠 比空間佢習慣更好 會周圍柯除外"},{"pid":"32e2a4b87fed366f51344b4162dc54ec40bbc0e2","tid":494980,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T11:22:08.000Z","msg":"比時間佢自己適應下環境"},{"pid":"bbc0814a8b88dd215c28734777a7b90665d9973f","tid":494980,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"我之前領一歲貓困左